SUMMARY:SALSA Society Thursdays at Thrōw Social Miami Wynwood!
DESCRIPTION:Miami Salsa Events and Thrōw Social Miami proudly present: \nSALSA Society Thursdays!!\nMarch 5th\nMarch 12th\nMarch 19th \nGet your dance shoes ready and come join us at Wynwood’s hottest and newest open venue! Fully remodeled and beautiful! Invite your friends and families for our grand opening of Salsa Society as we take you on a musical journey of Salsa while you dance the night away\, socialize and mingle\, enjoy the amazing drinks and food\, and have an amazing Salsa Night in the heart of Wynwood! \n8pm: Free Salsa Class by none ohter than Mel In Motion! \nMusic by:\nDJ Mike Caldero Y Sus Bravos!\nCongas: Eduardo Cano\nTimbales: Joseph Watts \nFREE COVER ALL NIGHT! \nFor more info visit us on www.miamisalsaevents.com
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-society-thursdays-at-throw-social-miami-wynwood/2026-03-26/
LOCATION:THRōW Social Miami Wynwood\, 2335 North Miami Avenue\, Miami\, FL 33127\, Miami\, FL\, 33127\, US
CATEGORIES:Miami
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/TSM_Salsa-Society-Thursdays_FB.png
END:VEVENT
