SUMMARY:Canada Salsa Bachata Kizomba Festival - 10% Discount
DESCRIPTION:Use promo code GOLATINDANCE2026 to save 10% on your pass!\nToronto’s biggest Salsa\, Bachata & Kizomba experience is BACK — and **Early-Bird passes are now ON SALE at 50% OFF** (our lowest price ever!) for a **limited time only**! 🚨✨\nGet ready for an unforgettable weekend featuring:\n💃 World-class workshops with top local & international artists\n🔥 Spectacular shows & competitions\n🎯 Jack & Jill Bachata Competition\n🎤 Live concerts\n🎶 Social dancing until **7AM** every night!\n🎧 **Confirmed Artists & DJs include:**\nDJ York • DJ Alexio\n🎤 Kewin Cosmos (Concert) • Shama (Concert)\nDiago Camilo (Colombia) • Jhoana Palhua (Peru)\nRene Esquea (USA) • Barbara Aristigueta (USA)\nDuda Maciej & Adriana Drozdowicz (Poland)\nLisa Karst (Germany) • Alan Soldek & Cristina Camarasa (Spain)\nCristian Vergari (Italy) • Marta Lipska (Lithuania)\n📍 Sheraton Centre Toronto
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/canada-salsa-bachata-kizomba-festival-10-discount/
LOCATION:Sheraton Centre Toronto\, 123 Queen Street West\, Toronto\, M5H 2M9\, Canada
CATEGORIES:Toronto
END:VEVENT
