SUMMARY:Sweetlead Sunday Afternoon Salsa Social
DESCRIPTION:Sweetlead Sunday afternoon salsa socials since 2016. \nRelaxed\, daytime salsa social dancing.\nNo classes just pure social dancing from 4pm to 7pm. #sweetleadss \n𝗣𝗥𝗜𝗖𝗘\n£8 on the door \n𝗦𝗡𝗔𝗖𝗞 𝗧𝗔𝗕𝗟𝗘 (𝗼𝗽𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝗮𝗹)\nOur Sunday afternoon socials are a relaxed affair and people often bring snacks/ drinks to share.\nSome people even bake!\nEverything on the communal snack table is free for everyone to enjoy. \n𝗙𝗜𝗡𝗗𝗜𝗡𝗚 𝗨𝗦\nAddress: Christ’s College\, East End Road\, Finchley\, London\, N2 0SE \nNearest tube:\nFinchley Central (Northern Line)\nBuses: 112\, 143\, 232\, 643 and 653\nParking:\n100+ free parking spaces on site \nThe entrance is next to the Crematorium (to the right).\nContinue down the drive to the mini roundabout and we are in the building just ahead.\nThere are multiple parking areas on the site. \nNote\, children are welcome to our Sunday afternoon events at no additional charge. \n𝗠𝗨𝗦𝗜𝗖 𝗣𝗢𝗟𝗜𝗖𝗬\n90% salsa\, 10% Kizomba/bachata/cha cha \n𝗤𝗨𝗘𝗦𝗧𝗜𝗢𝗡𝗦/ 𝗤𝗨𝗘𝗥𝗜𝗘𝗦\nEmail info@northlondonsalsaclub.com or call 07587781288.
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/sweetlead-sunday-afternoon-salsa-social/2026-04-06/
LOCATION:Christ’s College\, East End Road\, N2 0SE\, East End Road\, Finchley\, London\, N2 0SE\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:London
END:VEVENT
