DESCRIPTION:Join us Monday nights for *3 levels* of Salsa & Bachata classes at Golden City Dance Collective! Classes are run as a *month-long series*\, drop-ins welcome in weeks 1 & 2 of the month. \n7-8PM: BACHATA CLASSES\n-Bachata 1\n-Bachata 2\n-Bachata 3 \n8-9PM: SALSA CLASSES\n-Salsa 1\n-Salsa 2\n-Salsa 3 \n9-10PM: SALSA & BACHATA PRACTICA
