SUMMARY:Salsa Practica
DESCRIPTION:Salsa is a Latin dance influenced by several styles\, like mambo and rumba. The dance is characterized by energetic footwork\, spins\, and turns. We teach On1\, which is characterized by a lot of spinning and dancing in a slot (unlike Cuban or Cumbia styles). \nAge Requirement: All Ages\nMusic: TBA\nPrice: $15 ($5 with a valid student ID for all DJed events)
