SUMMARY:SALSA MONDAYS with Tomaj & Stasha!
DESCRIPTION:SALSA DANCING in ORINDA on MONDAY NIGHTS!\nClasses & Social Dancing for ALL Levels! \nLearn to dance Salsa with master instructors Tomaj and Stasha! Learn partnering skills\, leader and follower techniques\, rhythm\, timing\, foot work and ladies styling! These classes are highly popular & attended by students of ALL levels. Learn to look good\, get some great exercise\, and have a lot of FUN! \nNo Experience necessary. No Partner required! \nDROP-INS always welcome.\nDISCOUNT 10-Class Cards & COUPLES DISCOUNTS always Available! \nMondays: \nBeginning Class 7:00-8:00pm \nIntermediate/Advanced Class 8:00-9:00pm \nSocial Dancing before and after each class. \nWilder Art & Garden Center\, 20 Orinda Fields Lane\, Orinda \nInfo: 415-505-3536
